Package edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.strategy.weatherparsing

Class WeatherData

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cs505.finalproject.group4.patterns.strategy.weatherparsing.WeatherData

  • public class WeatherData
extends java.lang.Object
    WeatherData class will handle the Temperature and Humidity which is fetched from the OpenWeatherMAP API. The temperature is handled in terms of Minimum, Maximum and Average Temperature. There is a constructor for the WeatherData which is initialized to 0.
    Version:
    2.0
